  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC449">
        <l>peyar nilaik kiḷaviyi ṉāa kunavuñ</l>
	<l>ciṉai nilaik kiḷaviyi ṉāa kunavun</l>
	<l>toṉṉeṟi moḻivayi ṉāa kunavu</l>
	<l>meynnilai mayakki ṉāa kunavu</l>
	<l>mantirap poruḷvayi ṉāa kunavu</l>
	<l>maṉṟi yaṉaittuṅ kaṭappā ṭilavē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/248/mode/1up">248</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/250/mode/1up">250</ref>.</p>
<p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, orucār vaḻukkāttal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : ivai mēṟ kūṟappaṭṭa ilakkaṇattiṉai yaṉṟi yākāmaiyila eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>'peyarnilaikkiḷaviyiṉ' eṉpatu, īṇṭu uyartiṇaip peyarai yāyiṟṟu. avvuyartiṇaippeyar uyartiṇaip peyarmēl vaḻaṅkappaṭutaliṉṟiyum amaiyumeṉṟavāṟu. nampi eṉṉum uyartiṇaippeyar oru yāṉai mēlāṉum, oru kōḻi mēlāṉum, piṟavaṟṟiṉ mēlāṉum niṟkum. naṅkai eṉpa oru kiḷiyaiyum eṉpatu.</p>
<p>iṉic, ciṉainilaik kiḷaviyiṉāvaṉa kaṭappāṭiṉṟi varumāṟu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC449-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'veṇkoṟṟap paṭaittalaivaṉ'</l>
<l>'veḷḷēṟak kāviti'</l></lg>
<p>eṉpaṉa.</p>
<p>ivaṟṟai muṉṉark kiḷaviyākkattuc ciṟappuppeyar niṉṟavaḻi iyaṟpeyar vaittukkūṟupa eṉṟār ; iṉic ciṉaic coṟkaṇāyiṉ atu vēṇṭuvataṉṟu eṉpatu karuttu.</p>
<p>'toṉṉeṟi moḻivayi ṉāa kunavum' eṉpatu muṟṟuccol ; avaṟṟaiyum ivvāṟē collappaṭutaliṉ ipporuḷa eṉṟōr kaṭappāṭila eṉṟār.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'āṟṟuṭ cetta verumai ūrkkuyavaṟ kiḻuttal kaṭaṉ' eṉavum, 'yāṭṭuḷā ṉiṉṉurai tārāṉ' eṉavum varum. piṟavum aṉṉa.</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC449-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'meynnilai mayakki ṉāa kunavum'</l> <p>eṉpatu, mēl,</p>
<l>'takutiyum vaḻakkun taḻīiyiṉa voḻukum'</l>	<p>[tol. col. kiḷavi - 17]</p></lg>
<p>eṉpuḻi, maṅkala marapiṉāṉum kuḻūviṉvanta kuṟinilai vaḻakkiṉāṉum kūṟappaṭumeṉṟāraṉṟē, iṉi, avai avvāṟaṉṟit tattam ilakkaṇattāṉuñ collappaṭum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : cuṭukāṭṭai naṉkāṭu eṉṉātu cuṭukāṭu eṉṟum, cettārait tuñciṉār eṉṉātu cettār eṉṟum kūṟavum amaiyum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>iṉi,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC449-Iḷam-cit3">
<l>'mantirap poruḷvayi ṉāakunavum'</l></lg> <p>eṉpatu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC449-Iḷam-cit4">
<l>'niṟaimoḻi mānta rāṇaiyiṟ kiḷanta</l>
<l>maṟaimoḻi tāṉē mantira meṉpa'</l> <p>[tol. poruḷ. ceyyu - 171]</p></lg>
<p>avai, kūṟappaṭṭa eḻuvakai vaḻuviṟṟīrntu varuka eṉṟa kaṭappāṭila eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>avai,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC449-Iḷam-cit5">
<l>'tiritiri cuvākā kaṉṟu koṇṭu</l>
<l>kaṟavaiyum vattikka cuvākā'</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟāṟpōla varum.</p>
<p>ic cūttirattiṟkup piṟitumōr poruḷ uraippārum uḷar. ituvum meyyurai pōlum eṉpatu.	(53)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

